    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, r u saying that religious freedom isn't a right then? like, if a group has a deeply held belief, isn't it kind of unfair for the government to just force them to violate their conscience? it feels like there has to be a balance between secularism and actually respecting people's rights.",
